        <updateDate>2008-10-21T14:43:54Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Evacuees Assistance Act of 2008 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow individual taxpayers a tax credit, up to $2,000, for uncompensated travel expenses (including meals and lodging) incurred due to a mandatory evacuation of a disaster area.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
